su često nepravilno napisane

00:13:10.872 --> 00:13:13.088
i često koriste LOLcat internet žargon,

00:13:13.088 --> 00:13:15.584
ali ipak

00:13:15.584 --> 00:13:20.023
veoma cene to, zahvalni su

00:13:20.023 --> 00:13:23.577
pa znam da sam na pravom putu

00:13:23.577 --> 00:13:27.144
kako treba da predajemo nauku.

00:13:27.144 --> 00:13:30.080
